.TP
\f[CR]pdfa\f[R]
adds to the preamble the setup necessary to generate PDF/A of the type
specified, e.g.\ \f[CR]1a:2005\f[R], \f[CR]2a\f[R].
If no type is specified (i.e.\ the value is set to True, by e.g.
